      "content": "cool. the app is at localhost:3000. we're using playwright for the tests. i'll leave the specific test logic to you. just make sure the script covers the login, the dashboard loading, and the final checkout completion. remember, the main thing is that the CI pipeline needs that green checkmark. if the tests fail even once, the build fails and we're stuck. just give me the test script.+",
